<HL>
   Unocal Building Signals Landmark Duels
   ---
   Issue Is of Structures
   Still Relatively Young
   ----
   By Ross Miller
   Special to The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
03/13/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A7A
</SO>
<CO>
   UCL
</CO>
<MS>
